---
title: Turkish Lamb Meatballs with Herby Couscous
description: Our Turkish spice blend is full of warm flavors like allspice and cumin for a Middle Eastern twist on traditional meatballs. Earthy, sweet parsnips give this sauce another unique spin. Served on a bed of fluffy couscous, this is a hearty, satisfying dish you’ll love to curl up with.
